PrecisRegulations Amending the LIVESTOCK AND POULTRY CARCASS GRADING REGULATIONS by adding guinea fowl to the list of poultry species eligible for grading, by clarifying certain labelling requirements and by allowing the kidneys to be left in a duck carcass weighing less than three kilograms, provided it is so indicated on the product label.

precis:
Regulations Amending the LIVESTOCK AND POULTRY CARCASS GRADING REGULATIONS
by adding guinea fowl to the list of poultry species eligible for grading,
by clarifying certain labelling requirements and by allowing the kidneys to
be left in a duck carcass weighing less than three kilograms, provided it
is so indicated on the product label.
